name: Commissioned portrait - female/garland

Please get in touch if you have any ideas you would like to see on paper for your home or as a present.

name: FARAH Tee

We love this for the guys! Smart casual FARAH light blue with navy and cream t-shirt.

Perfect for the autumn season, keeping you snug but stylish.

Original antique ornament in the form of a young boy working with his blue spade. The boy's rosy cheeks and locks make us coo!

Operates on an electric plug as well as batteries if you wanted it to be a portable radio.

This adorable jug in the form of a traditional round lady, holding a bunch of flowers is one of our favourite Antique products.

This ornament is in a great condition with no damage or fading to it.  

Perfect for pouring your milk at the Tea party you host! Also would make a great present.

We will take orders for a PRINT of this painting for Â£20.

This striking clock would make a great focal point and subject which makes it unnecessary to repair if it's for an interior design purpose.

This cream/baige Ladies jacket complete with a silk cream hankie has come from America which makes this an individual Vintage jacket.

Original Southern Comfort whisky advertisement mirror, print on Logo and wooden frame. 

A4 size approx. Brass hole ready to hang up.

name: *RARE* 1950'S Rosebud Doll
description:
Original British hard plastic Rosebud baby doll. 

6" in height she has blue sleep eyes, nice colouring and moulded curls. 
Wearing a wool nappy with silk ribbon.  

She has the earlier marking "Rosebud - Made in England" in capitals rather than the later script logo. Which confirms her originality.

name: Harlequin Jester
description:
25 year old Vintage Dynasty Doll Mardi Gras style Harlequin Jester with silk costume and gold shoes in excellent condition.

25" high approx.

Porcelain face and feet.

name: 70's Retro Cocktail Glasses
description:
Very popular with our customers, this set of 4 Red Cocktail glasses are from the 1970's and give the illustration that they are made out of plastic. 

Could be used to present Dessert as well as being used for a  tipple. 

The glasses unique shape make this an exciting set to own and host with!

name: Vintage Lemon Cardigan
description:
We love this cute summery Nylon cardigan with its pastel lemon colour and marble effect buttons.
